    "detail": "Definitely Five Star all the way! One of the most enjoyable and nicest hotels I have stayed at in the Shearton Chain. Sadly, I had only booked the one night and moved to another hotel for the remainder of my time in Surabaya. Totally professional, courteous and friendly staff. I entertained local friends in the various restaurants for breakfast, lunch and dinnmerand they were most impressed. The AGODA special rate Deluxe room was excellent value and was spacious and most comfortable. If money is not a major concern, I would very strongly recommend Sheraton Surabaya Hotel & Towers to everyone.",
