  {
    "hotel_id": "7575",
    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/bumi-surabaya-city-resort/hotel/surabaya-id.html",
    "name": "Bumi Surabaya City Resort",
    "detail": "Best hotel in Surabaya. The room is VERY SPACIOUS. Far more spacious than most 5-star hotels. Air conditioning is very good, the windows are clean. Beds are very comfortable and the rooms are very comfortable. Bathroom and showers are excellent, and also very spacious. Water pressure is good, and water temperature is very good. Excellent breakfast, the best nasi goreng ever. Very complete breakfast, all delicious and all very fulfilling. The quality of breakfast is very excellent, better than most 5-star hotels. Very nice swimming pool and very nice gym facilities. Excellent staff that are all very friendly, better than most 5-star hotels in big towns such as Jakarta and Surabaya. I would like to compliment Mas Joe and Mas Nyoman as managers, and also Mba Nenny in reception, for their excellent service during my multiple visits to the hotel. Location is close to the city, which is very good.",
