  {
    "hotel_id": "625695",
    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/ibis-surabaya-city-center-hotel/hotel/surabaya-id.html",
    "name": "ibis Surabaya City Center Hotel",
    "detail": "I think I would simply say that the hotel's main point would be cleanliness and simplicity. Especially for business travellers even when my last stay there for holiday purposes. Everything was functional, room was clean and the bed was surprisingly comfortable. The bathroom is rather small for a big guy like me, but, it was practical and everything was in working order. Another best plus of the hotel is its breakfast selection. For a fourstar leaning to budget operation, Ibis Surabaya City Center has quite a wide selection of breakfast, both local and western buffet menu. All in all, it was an enjoyable stay. Really worth the pricetag, if not more. Thank you and keep it up. Hendrawan.",
